scopecontent.p:
This is a collection of papers of Helen and Ira Wolfert and of their son Michael
                    Wolfert. Helen and Ira Wolfert materials include: typed and handwritten
                    manuscripts of stories, poems, plays, novels, and reviews; notes for writings;
                    articles and clippings; copies of published articles, reviews, and poems;
                    personal and professional correspondence; financial materials; diaries;
                    photographs and negatives. Of note are letters between the Wolferts during Ira
                    Wolfert's time as a war correspondent. Michael Wolfert materials include
                    typescripts; handwritten notes for writings; diaries; clippings and extracts of
                    news items; financial materials; and a small amount of correspondence.
